x86/nospec, objtool: Introduce ANNOTATE_IGNORE_ALTERNATIVE

To facillitate other usage of ignoring alternatives; rename
ANNOTATE_NOSPEC_IGNORE to ANNOTATE_IGNORE_ALTERNATIVE.

